import React from "react" import {Col, Row} from "react-bootstrap" import {Link } from "react-router-dom" import dayjs from "dayjs" const List = (props) => { // console.log(props) const renderList = () => { return (<>
{props.orchestra}
{props.time}
{`${props.country} ${props.city}`}
{`${props.day}`}
{`${dayjs(props.month).format('MMMM')}`}
{`${props.year}`}
 ) } return (<> {renderList()} ) } export default List
